# ===========================
# Android Build Artifacts
# ===========================

# Build output directories (the main bloat ~20-30MB per project)
**/build/

# Gradle cache and wrapper downloads
**/.gradle/

# Local machine-specific SDK path (never share this)
**/local.properties

# IntelliJ/Android Studio module files
**/*.iml

# Android Studio captures (profiler data, etc.)
**/captures/

# Android Studio generated files
**/.idea/assetWizardSettings.xml
**/.idea/deploymentTargetSelector.xml
**/.idea/deviceManager.xml

# OS generated files
**/.DS_Store
**/Thumbs.db